he job you and your family have the right to enjoy these benefits because of the strength of our membership as long as you are a teamster member you are eligible for deals on products and services that are not available to the general public teamster job bank teamster members their spouses children and friends can have easy access to union job opportunities with good contracts and sound benefits jrh scholarship the james r hoffa memorial scholarship fund provides scholarships to the children and financial dependents of teamsters worker training programs the teamsters niehs worker training grants program provides safety and health courses that teamsters need disaster relief the teamsters disaster relief fund assists members who have suffered a loss from a disaster long after the media has forgotten teamster privilege credit card teamster privilege credit cards offer features like  usbased phone customer service and  fraud liability if your card is lost or stolen  plus after just  months as a teamster privilege cardholder you may be eligible for hardship grants in times of need member benefits life and accident insurance these teamster privilege insurance plans help to provide financial security for you and your family  press please visit our press center for the latest news information and other resources go to the magazineread the teamster magazine social networks like us on facebook follow us on twitter watch us on youtube follow us on instagram listen to the podcast sorry but we failed to add you to the list please try again or contact  sign up for action alerts please leave blank name cell phone number email address zip code mobile alerts from teamsters periodic messages msg  data rates may apply text stop to  to stop receiving messages text help to  for more informationterms  conditions loading thanks for signing up news  teamsters teamsters north americas strongest union james p hoffa general president ken hall general secretarytreasurer home news july   local 