ss they are the only workers on broadway without a union without healthcare and without retirement programs as broadway producers push back on the union drive many supporters are looking back to the campaign that film and television casting directors waged a decade ago for a union casting directors won that fight with the support of hollywood’s great actors directors and other creative professionals like the broadway fairnessforcasting campaign these celebrity supporters spoke about the essential role that casting directors play in the creative process and the solidarity they felt for their colleagues  here are some of those statements of support this weeks teamster news for july  here are the news items of interest to teamsters for this week july july   teamsternationunfisafewaylaw enforcementcity workerscorrectional officerstransit workersmckessonopioid crisisceo payken hallnlrbwaldnerslockoutairport workersupsairline mechanicsitfxpohaitigarment workerssri lankanikecambodianaftaworld bankimfright to workunion duesminimum wagepaid family leaveuawtwuufcwunite hereiamobamacareovertimelgbttax cutsmissouriprivatizationsanctuary citiesamerican airlinesnissanfacebookdisneyiowanew jerseynew yorklouisianaboliviamexicolocal local local local local local local local  pages     … next › last » videos james hoffa on mornings with maria we have to get jobs back play video port driver daniel uaina speaks at la port strike  fight for justice play video teamsters fight to get fired xpo drivers’ jobs back play video asm houghtaling stands with locked out shore point workers play video teamsters take on amerisourcebergen’s role in fueling opioid epidemic play video teamsters rally demand changes at xpo play video trucking company steals  teamster local  workers wages play video general president james p hoffa on sunday morning futures with maria bartiromo play video general president james p hoffa interview on cnbcs closing bell play video general president james p hoffa interview o